{"tid":44200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好人難做，大家評理！","createTime":"2016-12-18T05:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T03:12:38.000Z","uid":18320,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"086022f040beaf4cba50c80589d097b1ba7cd820","tid":44200,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"話說今日final 見到有個人溫書，佢將d notes 放曬係枱到，之後好專注咁做d練習，見到佢溫堆海量既notes，我就想提佢邊到比較重要（自己整既精華notes)，但無理由將我d心血就咁送比人所以我就想小小地煩一煩佢，如果佢仲係好專注既話，我就提佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後我就行埋去掃撚曬d notes落地下之後同條友講：你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你收皮啦！柒頭，你冇撚用嫁喇！等爛grade 啦死垃圾傻閪。之後指撚住佢個柒頭講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後比佢車鳩左一巴，好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以話呢，好人難做呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉，大家評下理！"},{"pid":"2acfb6679daf39cc20ed539701c8e18bd660c2c6","tid":44200,"uid":33031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"fb356675db8e4c19fd5c4f0478e63763cccf9769","tid":44200,"uid":15851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"7.5/10 唔錯 幾抵死"},{"pid":"db172a3771fe914f8eab756eb6a808cd8f9feb87","tid":44200,"uid":64816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢同你諗法一樣, 冇理由就咁送個初吻畀你<br />\n所以車你一巴之後再錫你一啖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e30863255d94bacfd3e09177cbfe08889f5a166","tid":44200,"uid":